{"ID":"20240513144808-hsj4on7","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"icon":"opengl.png","id":"20240513144808-hsj4on7","title":"窗口渲染","type":"doc","updated":"20240513144900"},"Children":[{"ID":"20240513144900-nbo456m","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513144900-nbo456m","updated":"20240513144900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"窗口成功创建后，便可以进行绘制了。通常我们会使用一个循环绘制，"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"code","TextMarkTextContent":"glfwWindowShouldClose"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"​ 可用于判断窗口是否应当关闭。"}]},{"ID":"20240513144900-kpt2aob","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20240513144900-kpt2aob","updated":"20240513144900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"我们通过将颜色缓冲区的颜色清空成一个纯色，使窗口显示一个纯色的背景。"}]},{"ID":"20240513144900-syh0ebq","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","IsFencedCodeBlock":true,"Properties":{"id":"20240513144900-syh0ebq","updated":"20240513144900"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"Yysr"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"// 窗口事件绑定完成\n// 窗口绘制循环\nwhile (!glfwWindowShouldClose(window))\n{\n    // 清空缓冲区\n    glClearColor(1, 1, 1, 1);\n    glClear(GL_COLOR_BUFFER_BIT);\n    // 绘制开始\n    // 绘制结束，交换后台缓冲区\n\tglfwSwapBuffers(window);\n\t// 处理输入事件（键盘、鼠标等）\n\tglfwPollEvents();\n}\n// 清理资源并结束\nglfwDestroyWindow(window);\nglfwTerminate();\n"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```"}]}]}